// File: src/il/runtime/defs/classes/input_game.def
// Purpose: Input, game, graphics, and 2D physics runtime class declarations.
// Key invariants:
//   - Included in declaration order by src/il/runtime/runtime.def.
//   - Class blocks remain balanced within this fragment.
// Ownership/Lifetime:
